-----------------------------------------------------------

Happy Friday and welcome back to The Daily Courant, your afternoon digest o=
f Puck=E2=80=99s best
new reporting.

=C2=A0

First up today, Matt Belloni sits down with Netflix chief content officer B=
ela Bajaria=E2=80=94charged with deploying/disbursing the streamer=E2=80=99=
s $18 billion content budget=E2=80=94for a remarkably candid conversation o=
n everything from the streaming behemoth=E2=80=99s live sports strategy to =
Greta=E2=80=99s Imax deal, the Emilia P=C3=A9rez Oscar scandal, the
Prince doc, and so much more.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

Plus, below the fold: Peter Hamby chronicles Rick Caruso=E2=80=99s frenetic=
 return to California politics and a possible showdown with Kamala Harris. =
John Ourand digs into ESPN and MLB=E2=80=99s hardball media rights negotiat=
